PART I: THE LAYERS
═══════════════════════════════════════════


T: THE SUBSTRATE
================

Before distinction, there is T.

T is not a dimension. T is not a coordinate.
T is the substrate. The canvas. The precondition for change.

Without T, there is no before and after.
Without before and after, there is no change.
Without change, there is no distinction.
Without distinction, there is no computation.
Without computation, there is no existence.

    T → change → distinction → computation → existence

T is not something you travel through. It is something you
exist on. You don't route through time. You unfold on it.

T flows forward because distinction is irreversible.
You can't un-distinguish. You can't un-know.
This is not a constraint we impose. This is the definition.

    T is the white room.
    X, Y, Z are the marks on it.

The name reads X-Y-Z-T. The deepest thing comes last
because it's so fundamental you almost forget to mention it.
Like a painter forgetting to mention the canvas.


LAYER 0: DISTINCTION
====================

The universe begins with one act: distinguishing.

    0 | 1

That's it. Not "zero" and "one". Not "false" and "true".
Just: THIS or NOT-THIS. The first cut.

Everything else is positions of this distinction.

    {2} — the cardinality of distinction

T is what makes this possible. Without T, there is no moment
where 0 becomes 1. No moment where the first cut is made.
T is Layer -1. Distinction is the first act performed on it.
If you cannot distinguish, you cannot compute. You cannot exist.


LAYER 1: POSITION
=================

A distinction alone means nothing.
Two distinctions still mean nothing.
Meaning requires PLACE.

    (x, y, z) on T — a point in the lattice, at a moment

    x = input channel      (which signal)
    y = time slot          (when in cycle)
    z = depth              (derived from what)

    T indexes the state. T is not a position in the lattice.
    T is WHEN this lattice state exists. The same (x, y, z)
    at different T is not the same point — it's the same
    address in a different state. Because different things
    happened to get there. History matters. That's what T records.

The value at position (x,y,z) at state T is either 0 or 1.
The position IS the meaning. There is no lookup table.
There is no "what does address 0x7F3A mean?"
The address IS the semantics.

    {3} — the minimum structure that gives position meaning

Two points define a line. Three points can define a plane.
{2} is the distinction. {3} is the structure.
From {2,3}, all else follows.


LAYER 2: COLLISION
==================

Two signals exist at positions A and B.
They propagate. They meet at position C.

What happens?

    (A + B)²

That's not a formula we chose. That's what superposition DOES.
Expand it:

    A² + 2AB + B²

    A²  = self-energy of A (A alone)
    B²  = self-energy of B (B alone)
    2AB = interaction (COMPUTATION)

The interaction term 2AB is the product of the inputs.
Extracted purely from collision. No multiplication instruction.
No ALU. Just: waves met.

In 3D, three waves from three axes:

    (A + B + C)² = A² + B² + C² + 2AB + 2AC + 2BC

One junction. Three inputs. Three interaction terms.
N inputs → N(N-1)/2 cross-terms. Quadratic scaling
from linear hardware. That's the power of collision.

This is the ONLY operation in XYZT.
Everything else is topology.


LAYER 3: IMPEDANCE
==================

Not every path conducts.
Not every collision fires.

    Z(p) — the impedance at position p

    Z = 0:   superconductor. Signal passes fully.
    Z = max: insulator. Signal blocked. Bandgap.

Impedance is not a parameter. Impedance IS the substrate.
It determines:

    What propagates  (conductance = signal * (1 - Z/max))
    What reflects    (R = ((Z2-Z1)/(Z2+Z1))²)
    What stores      (high-Z boundaries trap energy = cavity = memory)
    What selects     (bandgap: energy below threshold = absorbed)
    What delays      (higher Z = slower propagation = timing control)

Without impedance, the lattice is a puddle.
Every signal goes everywhere. Nothing computes.
Impedance is what makes topology selective.

    Q = quality factor = how many round-trips before decay
    Q = 188 means 188 oscillations of coherent storage.
    Proven.

Alternating high-Z / low-Z = photonic crystal = bandgap.
Defect in crystal = cavity = memory cell.
Thin mirror between cavities = coupling = wire.
Impedance ratio at junction = weight in a neural network.

Impedance is how the lattice becomes a COMPUTER
instead of a RESONATOR.


LAYER 4: TOPOLOGY
=================

Which positions connect to which?
With what impedance?
That IS the program.

    MAJORITY(a, b, c):
        Wire a, b, c to junction J.
        Output = sign(a + b + c).

    AND(a, b):
        Majority(a, b, 0).

    OR(a, b):
        Majority(a, b, 1).

Same physical structure. Different wiring. Different function.
The topology is not DESCRIBING the program.
The topology IS the program.

No instruction fetch.
No decode.
No execute.

Topology exists. Computation happens.



